{
  "stem": "833.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, in my voice, he knew that-- that's what he told me later on-- that he knew that I knew a little bit more about the situation.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--I seen that this-- that's end.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The father of my-- of one of my-- of my closest friend, Eric Simon, Ernst Simon, who was-- who was a very wealthy businessman, called me up and said, Herbert, how do you see the situation?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I told him, Ernst Simon, if I would be you, I would pack up immediately and leave the country for good.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's what he did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had a month's time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He left four or five days later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it has changed--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Overnight!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Overnight!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have no conception of what can happen, if a city that was, for nearly 2,000 years, the capital of a country-- small, larger, very large, then smaller, but still the center of-- that created its own culture, with a certain [NON-ENGLISH] of people that create-- that created and kept this culture.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The people like Richard Strauss, with his operas, couldn't be successful in a city where there was not a huge population that supported it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It is-- it is not just the creation of artists, it's a creation that they need to address themselves to people who try to understand.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What happened to Vienna overnight was that it suddenly and immediately became a German provincial city, which it never was before, in which the hub of the city-- those who kept its culture-- were suddenly a bunch of outlaws.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That is not an exaggeration.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Those 180,000 Jews of Vienna became, overnight, complete outlaws.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They could be robbed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They could be mishandled.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They could be killed-- as they would.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They couldn't do-- anything could happen to them.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
